            <p>Comments on note from Charles Kingsley saying CD’s theory is not opposed to a high conception of the Deity.</p> 
<p>Mentions negative views of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> of Sedgwick, John Crawfurd, Roderick Murchison, John Phillips, and Joseph Prestwich.</p> 
